  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00250', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-113-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「很少有書光靠封面設計就大賣。但另一方面，卻有很多書因為封面設計失敗而滯銷。」 關於這段文句的旨意，下列何者最適當？', '["書籍內容比起封面設計更為重要", "封面設計不良可能會讓好書滯銷", "封面設計與內容都出色才能暢銷", "封面設計的成敗決定銷量的高低"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f3fed3528446", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c24fe4b6c105", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00251', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-113-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列選項「」中前後詞意相同的是：', '["「春秋」時節最適宜全家出遊／此人腹中自有「春秋」，對人總有褒貶", "這個社區的長者「早晚」都會在公園練氣功／無論是誰，「早晚」都得面對死亡", "張小姐是他的「紅顏」知己／「紅顏」棄軒冕，白首臥松雲——是李白對孟浩然的讚美", "在醫學院從事教學多年的李醫師已「桃李」滿門／名師「桃李」天下，一點都不令人意外"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f3fed3528446", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c24fe4b6c105", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00252', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-113-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的成語，使用最適當的是：', '["接待人員們「前倨後恭」，誠摯歡迎每位與會的嘉賓", "在這寒冷的天氣，樹林一片「枝葉扶疏」的蕭瑟景象", "飯店緊臨港灣，在頂樓可以俯瞰「滄海橫流」的美景", "這家商店的營運狀況已「江河日下」，不能跟以前相比"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f3fed3528446", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c24fe4b6c105", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
